1
00:01:25,450 --> 00:01:29,940
[Coroner's Diary]

2
00:01:30,740 --> 00:01:33,840
[Episode 32]

3
00:01:48,539 --> 00:01:51,360
I, daughter-in-law Shen Wan,
pay my respects to you, Father.

4
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:52,229
Chief General.

5
00:01:52,810 --> 00:01:53,960
I, Bai Feng,

6
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:54,970
kowtow to you.

7
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,450
His Majesty has decreed

8
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:08,009
that tomorrow at 6 a.m.,

9
00:02:08,130 --> 00:02:10,060
we shall leave the city for burial.

10
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,009
No wake

11
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:12,250
and no mourning?

12
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:13,680
His Majesty said that

13
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:17,320
Father died at the hands of
the nomadic enemies,

14
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:20,450
so holding a wake or mourning rite
would be a breach of propriety.

15
00:02:20,450 --> 00:02:23,050
How could His Majesty
speak such absurd words?

16
00:02:37,690 --> 00:02:38,370
Wan.

17
00:02:42,130 --> 00:02:43,010
Help me.

18
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:54,640
Father.

19
00:02:55,250 --> 00:02:56,290
This is Shen Wan,

20
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:58,840
the woman I've chosen as my wife.

21
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:00,970
If you suffered any injustice,

22
00:03:01,030 --> 00:03:03,130
the two of us will definitely
seek justice for you.

23
00:03:03,130 --> 00:03:04,640
Father, you've tragically passed away,

24
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:05,850
and I, Shen Wan, your daughter-in-law,

25
00:03:05,850 --> 00:03:07,500
have to perform an autopsy.

26
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,970
If there's any offense,

27
00:03:08,970 --> 00:03:10,500
please forgive me, Father.

28
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:14,930
Wan.

29
00:03:15,300 --> 00:03:16,480
We only have six hours.

30
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:17,420
Time is tight.

31
00:03:17,590 --> 00:03:18,380
Just tell me

32
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,930
what you need me to examine.

33
00:03:20,250 --> 00:03:21,290
I want to know

34
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:24,360
whether Father was truly killed
by the nomadic enemies.

35
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:24,920
Okay.

36
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:26,320
I'll focus on examining the murder weapon

37
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,780
and the method of killing.

38
00:03:53,480 --> 00:03:54,800
There're a total of

39
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,329
17 wounds on Father's body.

40
00:03:57,079 --> 00:03:58,290
There are seven abrasions

41
00:03:58,290 --> 00:03:59,079
on the left shoulder,

42
00:03:59,079 --> 00:04:00,120
back,

43
00:04:00,290 --> 00:04:01,290
right wrist bone,

44
00:04:01,290 --> 00:04:02,570
and right calf.

45
00:04:02,570 --> 00:04:03,730
There're four impact or collision injuries

46
00:04:03,730 --> 00:04:05,570
on the chest and abdomen.

47
00:04:05,930 --> 00:04:07,420
The fatal wound is on the chest,

48
00:04:07,420 --> 00:04:09,820
caused by a sharp arrow
piercing the heart.

49
00:04:09,890 --> 00:04:11,420
Where was Father attacked?

50
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:13,970
Father was attacked
while on a border patrol,

51
00:04:13,970 --> 00:04:15,900
during a brief rest at a posthouse.

52
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,800
These are the grain husks I found

53
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,930
in Father's hair, used for horse feeding.

54
00:04:22,930 --> 00:04:24,080
Father's limbs

55
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:25,960
all have groove-shaped blood stains.

56
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:27,610
It appears that during the fight,

57
00:04:27,610 --> 00:04:28,960
someone threw bran in his face,

58
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:30,050
blocking his vision,

59
00:04:30,050 --> 00:04:31,400
then bound his limbs.

60
00:04:31,810 --> 00:04:33,159
This method of restraint

61
00:04:33,159 --> 00:04:35,130
could even control a bull.

62
00:04:40,860 --> 00:04:42,480
At that time,
Father was preparing to depart

63
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:46,740
and had sent his personal guard, Fan Xin,
to lead his horse from the backyard.

64
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:04,400
Father practiced martial arts continuously
throughout his life.

65
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:05,840
If it weren't for such a vicious method,

66
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:07,760
it would have been impossible
to subdue him.

67
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:09,960
Since the killer wanted to kill Father,

68
00:07:10,050 --> 00:07:12,610
they could have simply used
a rope to choke him.

69
00:07:12,610 --> 00:07:14,200
Why go to the trouble

70
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,370
to bind his limbs?

71
00:07:17,450 --> 00:07:18,200
Unless...

72
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:31,580
Why is this arrow wound

73
00:07:31,830 --> 00:07:33,560
different from ordinary ones?

74
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:35,480
It's a four-edged arrow.

75
00:07:39,010 --> 00:07:40,810
This is a weapon unique to
the nomadic enemies.

76
00:07:40,810 --> 00:07:41,760
Since the arrowhead is heavy

77
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:42,760
and has barbs,

78
00:07:43,250 --> 00:07:44,680
regular bows cannot shoot them.

79
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:47,880
This kind of arrow can only be fired
using a hand crossbow.

80
00:07:48,450 --> 00:07:49,960
Since they had already bound

81
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:51,440
Father's limbs with rope,

82
00:07:52,210 --> 00:07:53,550
wouldn't using a hand crossbow

83
00:07:53,550 --> 00:07:55,080
seem too deliberate?

84
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:58,940
Could it be that

85
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:00,720
they wanted to...

86
00:08:31,970 --> 00:08:33,640
They wanted to trap Father

87
00:08:34,590 --> 00:08:37,130
and then create the illusion of
him being shot through the heart.

88
00:08:37,130 --> 00:08:39,159
How could they act so boldly

89
00:08:39,539 --> 00:08:41,000
without anyone noticing?

90
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:42,679
By the time Fan Xin arrived,

91
00:08:42,679 --> 00:08:45,610
Father had already been shot
with the arrow and died.

92
00:08:56,860 --> 00:08:58,100
G-General...

93
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:04,130
General!

94
00:09:04,730 --> 00:09:05,930
When the killer left,

95
00:09:06,250 --> 00:09:06,890
they deliberately took the ropes

96
00:09:06,890 --> 00:09:08,750
that bound Father's limbs

97
00:09:08,850 --> 00:09:10,370
and left behind the four-edged arrow,

98
00:09:10,370 --> 00:09:11,680
as if to make it known that

99
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:13,450
it was done by the nomadic enemies.

100
00:09:13,450 --> 00:09:15,150
Was that a provocation against
the Shuoxi Army?

101
00:09:15,150 --> 00:09:17,040
The nomadic enemies have harbored a deep
and long-standing hatred for Father,

102
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:18,760
and they reward deeds with decapitation.

103
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:20,320
If it was really a provocation
from the nomadic enemies,

104
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:22,370
Father's body would certainly
not be intact.

105
00:09:22,370 --> 00:09:23,850
If it wasn't the nomadic enemies,

106
00:09:23,850 --> 00:09:25,320
then someone's trying to frame them.

107
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:27,490
The killer must be familiar with
the nomadic enemies' weapons.

108
00:09:27,490 --> 00:09:29,400
And they're also familiar with Father's
border patrol routes.

109
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,440
If that's the case,

110
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:33,210
those within the Shuoxi Army
are the most suspicious.

111
00:09:33,210 --> 00:09:34,730
It's time to meet Fan Xin.

112
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:37,970
When you passed through the posthouse,

113
00:09:37,970 --> 00:09:40,230
did you notice any traces of foreigners?

114
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:41,040
No.

115
00:09:41,490 --> 00:09:43,800
After the Crown Prince of Beidai
had an accident,

116
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:47,260
His Lordship had already ordered
strict border inspections.

117
00:09:47,490 --> 00:09:48,250
Then, General,

118
00:09:48,250 --> 00:09:50,560
did you get a good look at
the assassinator's appearance?

119
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:51,250
No.

120
00:09:51,970 --> 00:09:52,920
By the time I arrived,

121
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:54,180
the villains had already fled,

122
00:09:54,180 --> 00:09:56,640
and His Lordship and our men
were already...

123
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:59,330
General Fan, you've followed His Lordship
for many years.

124
00:09:59,330 --> 00:10:01,760
Have you ever seen the nomadic enemies
use rope formations

125
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:03,250
to encircle our soldiers and civilians?

126
00:10:03,250 --> 00:10:04,640
Rope formations?

127
00:10:05,850 --> 00:10:07,680
How does Your Highness know about this?

128
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:09,010
What do you mean by that?

129
00:10:09,250 --> 00:10:11,160
Young Marshal, you may not know this,

130
00:10:11,160 --> 00:10:12,560
but after you entered the capital,

131
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:13,960
His Lordship ordered the Tianshu Camp

132
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,280
to adapt our Zhou's meteor hammer

133
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:16,630
into a rope formation,

134
00:10:16,890 --> 00:10:19,010
specifically to force
the nomadic enemies to surrender.

135
00:10:19,010 --> 00:10:20,470
Besides the Tianshu Camp,

136
00:10:20,810 --> 00:10:22,250
who else knows about this formation?

137
00:10:22,250 --> 00:10:23,090
No one.

138
00:10:23,730 --> 00:10:25,130
Such a confidential formation

139
00:10:25,130 --> 00:10:26,970
is known only to His Lordship

140
00:10:27,590 --> 00:10:29,650
and the soldiers of the Tianshu Camp.

141
00:10:30,970 --> 00:10:32,000
The Tianshu Camp?

142
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:33,340
The Tianshu Camp

143
00:10:34,250 --> 00:10:35,850
is a special unit within the Shuoxi Army

144
00:10:35,850 --> 00:10:38,250
dedicated to assassinating enemy generals.

145
00:10:38,250 --> 00:10:39,110
Could it be that

146
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:41,370
there really is a traitor
within the Shuoxi Army?

147
00:10:41,370 --> 00:10:44,830
I never thought Father would die
at the hands of our own people.

148
00:11:12,210 --> 00:11:12,930
Father.

149
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:15,180
I, Shen Wan, hereby swear that

150
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:17,640
no matter who killed you,

151
00:11:18,090 --> 00:11:19,890
I will do everything in my power,

152
00:11:20,160 --> 00:11:21,590
together with Yan Chi,

153
00:11:21,970 --> 00:11:23,640
to avenge your bloodshed.

154
00:11:38,330 --> 00:11:40,050
[Funing Palace]

155
00:11:41,490 --> 00:11:43,440
I want to see my son.

156
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:45,040
Your Majesty, you cannot go!

157
00:11:45,420 --> 00:11:46,850
I want to see him.

158
00:11:46,880 --> 00:11:48,640
I beg Your Majesty
to prioritize your health above all else!

159
00:11:48,640 --> 00:11:49,840
My son...

160
00:11:49,970 --> 00:11:51,890
His Majesty arrives!

161
00:11:51,890 --> 00:11:54,220
-I need to see him.
-Mother!

162
00:11:54,510 --> 00:11:56,940
Mother, what are you trying to do?

163
00:11:56,970 --> 00:12:00,090
-What is this for, Mother?
-I want to see my son.

164
00:12:02,250 --> 00:12:03,730
Mother...

165
00:12:04,680 --> 00:12:05,880
All of you, step back.

166
00:12:06,560 --> 00:12:07,160
Quick.

167
00:12:07,850 --> 00:12:08,580
Mother.

168
00:12:08,730 --> 00:12:10,130
Please listen to me.

169
00:12:10,580 --> 00:12:11,640
Once you've

170
00:12:11,800 --> 00:12:13,520
fully recovered,

171
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:14,400
I'll

172
00:12:14,640 --> 00:12:16,040
personally accompany you

173
00:12:16,040 --> 00:12:18,400
to pay respects to Lin.
How does that sound?

174
00:12:18,400 --> 00:12:19,890
By then,

175
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:25,040
I will only be able to see a tomb.

176
00:12:25,040 --> 00:12:27,280
Don't stop me. Let me go!

177
00:12:27,280 --> 00:12:29,130
Mother. Mother.

178
00:12:29,130 --> 00:12:31,760
I had no choice in this matter, either.

179
00:12:32,210 --> 00:12:34,890
I am not only his elder brother,

180
00:12:35,250 --> 00:12:37,210
but also the ruler of this country.

181
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:40,920
I have to prioritize state affairs.

182
00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:42,670
What does that matter?

183
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:45,850
Lin was

184
00:12:46,490 --> 00:12:48,250
always loyal to you.

185
00:12:48,970 --> 00:12:50,670
Since your coronation,

186
00:12:51,230 --> 00:12:54,330
he guarded the border for over 20 years.

187
00:12:54,890 --> 00:12:56,810
Without your orders,

188
00:12:57,090 --> 00:13:00,120
he would never step a foot
beyond the Shuoxi border,

189
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:03,890
yet you always treated him
as a grave threat.

190
00:13:03,890 --> 00:13:05,970
Even after his death,

191
00:13:07,250 --> 00:13:09,980
you were stingy
in handling his funeral matters.

192
00:13:10,250 --> 00:13:12,370
What kind of emperor are you?

193
00:13:13,210 --> 00:13:15,630
What kind of elder brother are you?

194
00:13:15,800 --> 00:13:18,640
Mother, it's all my fault

195
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:21,640
for making you so heartbroken.

196
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:23,250
But Mother,

197
00:13:24,520 --> 00:13:26,800
Lin's sudden death

198
00:13:27,370 --> 00:13:31,680
will surely cause turmoil
at the border and in court.

199
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:33,210
I

200
00:13:33,370 --> 00:13:36,520
have no choice but
to simplify the funeral ceremonies.

201
00:13:36,520 --> 00:13:38,280
It's also to stabilize the border

202
00:13:38,280 --> 00:13:39,880
and ensure a smooth transfer

203
00:13:40,130 --> 00:13:43,370
of the Shuoxi Army's command.

204
00:13:44,040 --> 00:13:45,920
For the sake of your court,

205
00:13:47,370 --> 00:13:49,890
I've compromised again and again.

206
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:53,210
Am I supposed to compromise to the point
where I can't even

207
00:13:53,210 --> 00:13:54,970
see my son one last time?

208
00:13:56,130 --> 00:13:57,620
I might as well

209
00:13:57,970 --> 00:13:59,640
not serve as Empress Dowager anymore!

210
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:01,130
Mother!

211
00:14:05,560 --> 00:14:06,350
Is it that

212
00:14:07,370 --> 00:14:08,440
you only

213
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:11,040
care about Lin?

214
00:14:15,860 --> 00:14:18,180
Then what about me?

215
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:21,090
I am

216
00:14:23,010 --> 00:14:24,230
also your

217
00:14:26,210 --> 00:14:28,130
own flesh and blood.

218
00:15:05,970 --> 00:15:07,370
Are you saying the victim

219
00:15:07,370 --> 00:15:09,230
was Prince Jin's personal guard,

220
00:15:09,520 --> 00:15:10,640
Song Xiwen?

221
00:15:11,130 --> 00:15:13,890
A man who should have been imprisoned
in the Imperial Punishment Department

222
00:15:13,890 --> 00:15:16,620
ended up dead
at the Disgraced Prince's mansion.

223
00:15:17,370 --> 00:15:18,290
This matter

224
00:15:18,730 --> 00:15:20,160
is indeed suspicious.

225
00:15:22,680 --> 00:15:23,680
Your Majesty.

226
00:15:24,090 --> 00:15:26,130
The case of the Disgraced Prince
has long been concluded.

227
00:15:26,130 --> 00:15:28,470
Even if the deceased is truly Song Xiwen,

228
00:15:28,850 --> 00:15:31,520
he's merely a guard of no consequence
to the bigger picture,

229
00:15:31,520 --> 00:15:34,160
and escaping prison
is itself a capital offense.

230
00:15:34,160 --> 00:15:35,800
If we investigate this case further,

231
00:15:35,800 --> 00:15:38,250
stirring up settled matters

232
00:15:38,250 --> 00:15:39,370
and muddying clear waters,

233
00:15:39,370 --> 00:15:40,560
it would be unwise.

234
00:15:45,010 --> 00:15:45,810
Your Majesty.

235
00:15:46,090 --> 00:15:48,250
Marquis of Zhongyong makes a valid point.

236
00:15:48,250 --> 00:15:51,440
However, there are many rumors about
the male corpse found

237
00:15:51,440 --> 00:15:53,160
at the Disgraced Prince's mansion,
and if we neglect to investigate,

238
00:15:53,160 --> 00:15:54,680
I fear it will only
increase public suspicion

239
00:15:54,680 --> 00:15:58,480
and create new complications over
the Disgraced Prince's old case.

240
00:16:05,520 --> 00:16:06,520
Li Muyun.

241
00:16:08,800 --> 00:16:09,860
Yes, Your Majesty.

242
00:16:10,130 --> 00:16:13,010
This case was to be supervised
by your Supreme Court.

243
00:16:13,010 --> 00:16:15,660
How do you plan to handle it?

244
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:16,890
Your Majesty.

245
00:16:17,220 --> 00:16:18,110
I believe

246
00:16:18,370 --> 00:16:19,970
this case must be investigated.

247
00:16:19,970 --> 00:16:22,370
For the reputation of the Supreme Court,
it must be investigated.

248
00:16:22,370 --> 00:16:24,850
For the peace of the court,
it must be investigated even more.

249
00:16:24,850 --> 00:16:27,210
I am willing to thoroughly
investigate this case,

250
00:16:27,210 --> 00:16:28,400
so as to provide Your Majesty,

251
00:16:28,400 --> 00:16:29,490
the court,

252
00:16:30,040 --> 00:16:32,770
and the people of Zhou
with a proper explanation.

253
00:16:34,210 --> 00:16:35,950
Since Prince Rui has recently passed away,

254
00:16:35,950 --> 00:16:38,710
his son, Yan Chi, is in mourning.

255
00:16:39,040 --> 00:16:41,130
Thus, this case shall be

256
00:16:41,150 --> 00:16:43,680
handled by Prince Cheng, Yan Qi,
as the acting official.

257
00:16:43,680 --> 00:16:47,160
The Supreme Court shall assist
Prince Cheng in supervising this case.

258
00:16:47,160 --> 00:16:49,090
-Yes, Father.
-Yes, Your Majesty.

259
00:16:55,850 --> 00:16:59,260
[Funing Palace]

260
00:17:10,849 --> 00:17:12,480
Why have you returned so soon?

261
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:14,079
Is everything taken care of?

262
00:17:14,369 --> 00:17:16,230
Father has been properly buried.

263
00:17:16,890 --> 00:17:18,400
Given the current situation,

264
00:17:18,400 --> 00:17:19,530
the sooner I return,

265
00:17:19,680 --> 00:17:21,530
the more at ease His Majesty will be.

266
00:17:21,530 --> 00:17:22,460
Do you know that

267
00:17:22,810 --> 00:17:24,480
His Majesty has assigned Song Xiwen's case

268
00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:25,770
to Prince Cheng?

269
00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:26,800
I do.

270
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:29,960
Wan.

271
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:33,480
If I lose my position
at the Ministry of Justice

272
00:17:33,480 --> 00:17:35,210
and fail to inherit the throne,

273
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:37,770
would you still be willing to marry me?

274
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:41,480
I could open a medical clinic

275
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:43,530
and support you quite comfortably.

276
00:17:46,770 --> 00:17:47,630
Yan Chi.

